00:20:04,021 --> 00:20:06,342
And it's controlled by a MIDI Fighter 3D.

394
00:20:06,442 --> 00:20:07,322
So that's this device.

395
00:20:07,342 --> 00:20:08,503
It has 16 buttons on it.

396
00:20:09,143 --> 00:20:10,763
And they all glow and are shiny.

397
00:20:12,235 --> 00:20:16,778
And so it's usually a controller used by like producers to make music and stuff like that

